score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:17:42.000Z","msg":"開心一下都唔得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:01:15.000Z","msg":"開心下可以，但唔好唔記得自己仲輸緊好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3dc6c8ed6eb6d544b2e0c14fbecbbb1f4d37bf","tid":1752871,"uid":162906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"未贏, 大家繼續努力, 堅持,"},{"pid":"b588030b397eaadffc7f410e9f54b1d19ad74b89","tid":1752871,"uid":37054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"如果今次再好似14年咁全盤輸晒，真係睇唔到未來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次呢個政府唔會再比機會你做任何野，加上今次清算後會冇晒人<br />\n成代清洗"}]}